17.title: Episode #3.17
17.plot: Aysem is worried about her father. When she learns from Seval what happened, she is dismayed. Meanwhile, Aysem and Omer grow concerned about Hacer.

18.title: Episode #3.18
18.plot: Aysem is upset about Nail leaving Istanbul, but Omer has a different view of it. Reyhan and Mazhar are trapped in Sevinc's room. Zeyno goes missing.

19.title: Episode #3.19
19.plot: Aysem's friends prepare a surprise for her, but a mishap incapacitates them. To test Sevinc's feelings, Reyhan asks her to set her up with Sabri.

21.title: Episode #3.21
21.plot: Tolga tricks his captor. Seval discovers who killed Cevdet's brother. Fahriye learns Melda has a phobia and uses it to oust her unwanted roommates.

22.title: Episode #3.22
22.plot: Omer's exam results come back. Hacer gets in a fight at school and begs to return to her village. Sevinc gives Reyhan's mother an earful about Mazhar.

23.title: Episode #3.23
23.plot: Seeing Omer's arm bandaged, Aysem can't get angry at him. Despite all his efforts, Mazhar is crushed by Reyhan's father, but he refuses to be bowed.

24.title: Episode #3.24
24.plot: Zeyno's departure hurts Tolga, but he can do nothing. It's Valentine's Day and things are tense between Aysem and Omer, and Reyhan and Mazhar.

25.title: Episode #3.25
25.plot: Mentes' stabbing shakes everyone. All are curious about who did it. In fact, everyone thinks it was Melda, but nobody will come out and say it.

26.title: Episode #3.26
26.plot: Omer, Haluk, Mazhar, and Deniz's company gains fame thanks to the school Mazhar built. Hacer leaves home when she learns about her mother.
